videos.description: Western Kentucky's Justin Johnson catches fire early as he scores the first 8 points for the Hilltoppers.
videos.headline: Hilltoppers' Johnson opens game on 8-0 run

videos.description: The Hilltoppers' Justin Johnson gets his 10th point of the night early on after a fast-break dunk.
videos.headline: Johnson steals and slams

videos.description: Utah caps off a 9-0 run to tie the game at 25-25 with a Justin Bibbins steal and layup.
videos.headline: Bibbins bolts downcourt for fast-break score

videos.description: Western Kentucky's Lamonte Bearden hammers down a fast-break jam to tie the score at 32-32 moments before the halftime buzzer sounds.
videos.headline: Bearden throws it down before the buzzer

videos.description: Utah goes up by 2 with 38 seconds left after Justin Bibbins finds Tyler Rawson for a wide open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Rawson drains go-ahead 3 late

videos.description: Utah guard Justin Bibbins discusses the Utes NIT semifinal win over Western Kentucky and what it means to him.
videos.headline: Bibbins: 'It means the world' to advance to NIT final in senior season
